                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>An ephemeral, taloned hand grips the target, burning it with magical acid. The target takes 2d8 acid damage plus @Damage[floor(@item.level/2)d6[persistent,acid]] damage depending on its Reflex save. A creature taking persistent damage from this spell takes a –10-foot status penalty to its Speeds. @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spell-effects.Item.Spell Effect: Acid Grip]</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage and no persistent damage, and the claw moves it up to 5 feet in a direction of your choice.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and persistent damage, and the claw moves it up to 10 feet in a direction of your choice.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage and full persistent damage, and the claw moves it up to 20 feet in a direction of your choice.</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+2)</strong> The initial damage increases by 2d8, and the persistent acid damage increases by 1d6.</p>"
